Path: `users/{uid}` ‚Äî model: `lib/features/users/data/models/app_user.dart`.

## Customers

Use **`users/{uid}`** with **`role: customer`**.  
**No** global `customers` collection. **No** `salons/{salonId}/customers` cache in the current app.

## Fields

Document id = **`uid`**. Store **`uid`** in the document payload; do **not** introduce a separate **`id`** field for users.

uid: string
name: string
email: string
role: string (owner | admin | barber | customer | empty pending role selection)
salonId: string (nullable)
employeeId: string (nullable)
phone: string (optional)
isActive: boolean
createdAt: timestamp
updatedAt: timestamp

## Implemented vs Planned

**Implemented:** Fields above match `AppUser` / `UserRepository`.

**Planned:** `profileImageUrl`, `favoriteSalonIds` ‚Äî not in `AppUser` yet.
